Branch of the German military during World War II

This article delves into the air force of Germany as it existed before and during the [Second World War](/World_War_II). For those with a more contemporary interest, the current air force of Germany can be found under [German Air Force](/German_Air_Force). Should your curiosity extend to the earlier, First World War iteration of Germany's army-affiliated air force, you'll want to consult [Luftstreitkräfte](/Luftstreitkr%C3%A4fte). For any other, less specific interpretations, the term is further clarified at [Luftwaffe (disambiguation)](/Luftwaffe_(disambiguation)).

